  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A powerful magnetic field runs through this ancient stone, turning lumpen rock into something almost alive. The carver of this effigy is unknown.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>在强大磁场的力量下，原本沉重的巨石也展现出了近乎生命一般的神奇魅力。不知道这个雕塑究竟是出自何人之手。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>应用以改变你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "特殊的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>古老岩石中滿盈著強力的磁場，原本平凡無奇的石頭似乎有了生命。雕刻師身分已不可考。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
